# Screenshots folder

Audit and post-redesign screenshots are saved here, organised by date:

```
screenshots/
└── YYYY-MM-DD-<app-name>/
    ├── dashboard-1440px.png
    ├── dashboard-768px.png
    ├── dashboard-375px.png
    ├── ...other pages at each viewport...
    ├── refs/                     # Reference analysis from Phase 2
    │   ├── linear-1440px.png
    │   └── read-cv-1440px.png
    └── after/                    # Final screenshots after redesign
        └── ...
```

This folder is kept in git as a record of audits. If screenshots get too large, consider adding this path to `.gitignore`.
